Let's calculate the total earnings of the sign painter. We need to determine the sum of the digits of all house numbers on both sides of the street. Each side has 50 houses.</think>
\begin{align*}
\text{Total earnings} &= \text{Sum of digits of house numbers on the south side} + \text{Sum of digits of house numbers on the north side} \\
&= (\text{Sum of digits for the arithmetic sequence on the south side}) + (\text{Sum of digits for the arithmetic sequence on the north side}).
\end{align*}
<answer> $\boxed{1900}$ </answer>

